278
00:16:54,917 --> 00:16:58,125
It's nothing but you are attaching yourself to your Mother,

279
00:16:58,125 --> 00:17:00,333
you're just telephoning to Her.

280
00:17:01,500 --> 00:17:03,959
This is a telephone going to your Mother,

281
00:17:05,041 --> 00:17:06,500
that's all.

282
00:17:06,959 --> 00:17:08,583
You know I also play with you, I also say,

283
00:17:08,583 --> 00:17:11,000
"All right, I am giving you a bandhan."

284
00:17:12,125 --> 00:17:14,583
I am giving bandhan to Myself!

285
00:17:14,834 --> 00:17:16,208
It's a telephone call,

286
00:17:16,208 --> 00:17:18,083
just a telephone call.

