00:29:14,917 --> 00:29:16,500
his office has worked for us.

525
00:29:16,834 --> 00:29:18,583
He took all nonsensical people.

526
00:29:18,834 --> 00:29:20,959
If I told him, "This fellow is getting some ego,"

527
00:29:21,166 --> 00:29:22,917
he'll employ in his office.

528
00:29:23,125 --> 00:29:24,625
If I say, "This fellow has got bhoots,"

529
00:29:24,917 --> 00:29:26,375
he'll employ in his office.

530
00:29:26,625 --> 00:29:29,333
He has worked with such bhoots

531
00:29:29,333 --> 00:29:32,000
that I could not manage them even for a day.

532
00:29:35,458 --> 00:29:39,333
He tries his level best to go to people and tell them that,

533
00:29:39,583 --> 00:29:40,458
"See now, come."

534
00:29:40,458 --> 00:29:42,625
He has saved so many people

535
00:29:42,917 --> 00:29:44,959
by his sense, by his understanding;

536
00:29:45,333 --> 00:29:47,166
but the only thing is he, openly he doesn't lead,

537
00:29:47,166 --> 00:29:48,333
that's his mistake.

538
00:29:48,333 --> 00:29:49,375
He should openly tell,

539
00:29:49,375 --> 00:29:52,375
"You are a bhoot and get cured, then you'll be all right."

540
00:29:52,875 --> 00:29:53,542
But if you say,

541
00:29:53,542 --> 00:29:55,542
"Come here. You see, you are a bhoot, doesn't matter.

542
00:29:55,542 --> 00:29:57,792
I have got lemons, ..., chillies. You sit down."

543
00:29:57,792 --> 00:29:58,792
Then, "Mother,

544
00:29:58,792 --> 00:30:01,625
he is identifying himself with the greatest bhoot."

545
00:30:04,208 --> 00:30:05,875
Let us face it.

546
00:30:07,917 --> 00:30:11,208
If you have understanding of your leader,

547
00:30:11,542 --> 00:30:15,166
then you should know that I know better than you know

548
00:30:16,083 --> 00:30:17,583
about it.

549
00:30:19,667 --> 00:30:21,750
And this is very saddening sometimes.

550
00:30:21,750 --> 00:30:24,875
Why don't you understand the sheer goodness of a person?

551
00:30:26,000 --> 00:30:28,542
The amount of bhoots he has tolerated in his office,

552
00:30:28,542 --> 00:30:31,458
I tell you, I can't stand them for more than one day,

553
00:30:31,458 --> 00:30:32,959
some of them.

554
00:30:32,959 --> 00:30:35,667
So egoistical, some of them, off their heads,

555
00:30:36,375 --> 00:30:38,458
and some of them are so bhootish

556
00:30:39,208 --> 00:30:40,709
that even if they come downstairs

557
00:30:40,709 --> 00:30:44,458
I get a pain in the stomach, in My house.

558
00:30:44,458 --> 00:30:46,583
But he stood them.

559
00:30:47,208 --> 00:30:49,333
Why? What was the need?

560
00:30:49,999 --> 00:30:52,500
Just that he thought that he'd help them.

561
00:30:52,500 --> 00:30:54,583
Whenever I told him that "This person is bhootish,"

562
00:30:54,583 --> 00:30:57,250
I find him employed by Mr Gavin Brown.

563
00:30:58,834 --> 00:31:01,375
Then one day I had to tell him, "Sack all of them,"

564
00:31:01,375 --> 00:31:03,500
and they were sacked.

565
00:31:05,375 --> 00:31:07,834
Why do we have the maximum number of bhoots in England,

566
00:31:07,834 --> 00:31:09,542
I can't understand.

567
00:31:09,917 --> 00:31:11,792
Is it necessary to have them around?

568
00:31:14,125 --> 00:31:17,000
On the day when I am going I should not tell you these things,

569
00:31:17,000 --> 00:31:20,250
but when I go away I find these bhoots come back,

570
00:31:21,250 --> 00:31:24,917
and they become the causes, and the effects are shown.

571
00:31:26,208 --> 00:31:31,333
So I have to make a complete open picture to you

572
00:31:31,333 --> 00:31:35,333
to see that you can ascend to the highest of highest,

573
00:31:35,667 --> 00:31:38,458
being born on this great land of this country.

574
00:31:39,375 --> 00:31:42,959
But you can also go very down, I have seen that.

575
00:31:43,583 --> 00:31:45,959
Because you're always blaming someone,

576
00:31:48,583 --> 00:31:49,458
last of all Gavin,

577
00:31:49,458 --> 00:31:52,709
and this is the worst thing that you have done.

578
00:31:52,709 --> 00:31:54,792
Let anybody say that to Gregoire -

579
00:31:54,792 --> 00:31:56,709
he'll chop that person off ten times

580
00:31:56,709 --> 00:31:59,750
and bring that person to me in chopped stages!

581
00:32:01,458 --> 00:32:03,125
Really, I mean!

582
00:32:03,917 --> 00:32:05,333
He'll say, "What nonsense!

583
00:32:05,333 --> 00:32:07,500
All right, it's ... go ahead."

584
00:32:10,500 --> 00:32:11,750
You tell Mr.Warren,

585
00:32:11,750 --> 00:32:14,709
I don't know what he'll do with all of the Australian type.

586
00:32:15,041 --> 00:32:16,917
They are all gems, no doubt.

587
00:32:17,166 --> 00:32:20,375
But you deserve a man like Gavin.

588
00:32:20,750 --> 00:32:24,458
I thought, they are special people

589
00:32:24,709 --> 00:32:26,917
that I've worked for you so much,

590
00:32:27,125 --> 00:32:28,959
but I am amazed.

591
00:32:30,041 --> 00:32:33,458
The decent people don't need such leaders, do you?

592
00:32:34,709 --> 00:32:36,750
But the people who are decent now

593
00:32:36,750 --> 00:32:39,500
turn out to be Australians, surprisingly,

594
00:32:39,750 --> 00:32:41,834
the way they behave towards Me:

595
00:32:41,834 --> 00:32:44,125
so sweet they are, you'd be surprised,

596
00:32:44,125 --> 00:32:45,625
the children you know.

597
00:32:45,625 --> 00:32:49,208
Gavin, he bought some cups and saucers for Me

598
00:32:49,208 --> 00:32:52,458
because when I go there they thought they'll give Me tea

599
00:32:52,458 --> 00:32:54,208
in good cups and saucers.

600
00:32:54,208 --> 00:32:56,667
So he bought for all the centers one cup and saucer,

601
00:32:56,917 --> 00:32:57,917
good one.

602
00:32:57,917 --> 00:32:59,583
So the children, little, little children,

603
00:32:59,583 --> 00:33:00,750
they collected money;

604
00:33:00,750 --> 00:33:04,333
after all, Mother will have a cake, also must have a plate.

605
00:33:04,583 --> 00:33:07,875
So they sent a check here, just see - how sweet!

606
00:33:09,083 --> 00:33:11,667
But I never eat cakes, you know that, but still

607
00:33:13,417 --> 00:33:17,000
- so sweet the children, I should say.

608
00:33:19,750 --> 00:33:20,917
What is the reason?

609
00:33:20,917 --> 00:33:24,917
Why do we dominate or get dominated?

610
00:33:24,917 --> 00:33:25,917
Why?

611
00:33:29,583 --> 00:33:32,166
Again the cause.

612
00:33:32,750 --> 00:33:34,750
Go beyond the cause.

613
00:33:34,750 --> 00:33:38,417
I bless you again and again that when I come next time,

614
00:33:38,417 --> 00:33:41,291
see that you don't make any mistakes anymore.

615
00:33:41,291 --> 00:33:43,291
Meditate and meditate and meditate,

616
00:33:43,291 --> 00:33:45,041
and when you come to India some of you,

617
00:33:45,041 --> 00:33:47,999
I would like to show you as my prize things

618
00:33:47,999 --> 00:33:50,291
from where I've worked, you know.

619
00:33:50,542 --> 00:33:52,083
Even where I've not been, you see,

620
00:33:52,083 --> 00:33:56,417
somebody else has given realization to someone in Nepal,

621
00:33:56,417 --> 00:33:58,041
you see,

622
00:33:58,041 --> 00:33:59,834
and they are wonderful flowers;

623
00:33:59,834 --> 00:34:02,999
and here am I, something wrong with Me!

624
00:34:03,417 --> 00:34:05,250
Where I have worked,

625
00:34:07,166 --> 00:34:10,542
people are more worried about the causes.

626
00:34:10,834 --> 00:34:13,125
I have to really make a very, very

627
00:34:13,375 --> 00:34:17,041
straightforward appeal to you that now,

628
00:34:17,458 --> 00:34:19,458
grow within yourself.

629
00:34:19,458 --> 00:34:20,999
Are you magnanimous,

630
00:34:21,250 --> 00:34:22,166
are you generous,

631
00:34:22,166 --> 00:34:23,750
are you systematic?

632
00:34:24,417 --> 00:34:25,834
Are you impressive,

633
00:34:25,834 --> 00:34:26,709
are you kind,

634
00:34:26,709 --> 00:34:28,375
are you collective?

635
00:34:29,375 --> 00:34:32,999
Are you attached to all these nonsensical things still?

636
00:34:32,999 --> 00:34:34,875
Do you talk big,

637
00:34:34,875 --> 00:34:36,875
do you give big lectures?

638
00:34:38,041 --> 00:34:39,999
Humble down yourself,

639
00:34:40,625 --> 00:34:42,250
and then you'll see your greatness.

640
00:34:42,250 --> 00:34:44,667
Unless and until you put your head down to your heart,

641
00:34:44,917 --> 00:34:46,583
how will you see your Mother?

642
00:34:52,709 --> 00:34:54,917
I wish you all great luck now,

643
00:34:55,125 --> 00:34:59,250
and happy Christmas to you and happy New Year,

644
00:34:59,500 --> 00:35:02,500
and a very great New Year in spiritual growth.

645
00:35:02,792 --> 00:35:03,792
Let's show it.

646
00:35:03,792 --> 00:35:05,667
Let all of us decide today.

647
00:35:05,959 --> 00:35:08,250
Forget about your wives and husbands and children,

648
00:35:08,250 --> 00:35:09,583
and this and that nonsense.

649
00:35:09,583 --> 00:35:14,000
Now you are yogis, you are united with Divine.

650
00:35:14,333 --> 00:35:16,208
Grow in it, prosper in it.

651
00:35:17,375 --> 00:35:19,250
May God bless you all.

652
00:35:33,959 --> 00:35:35,667
Now the today's program

653
00:35:35,917 --> 00:35:37,834
should not be very big because we are not allowed

654
00:35:37,834 --> 00:35:39,083
lot of time,

655
00:35:39,083 --> 00:35:42,917
but it's nice that today we could have a little puja of farewell.

656
00:35:42,917 --> 00:35:45,542
But it should be a very small ... because it is,

657
00:35:45,542 --> 00:35:48,250
how much you receive is the point,

658
00:35:48,250 --> 00:35:51,583
because before going I don't want to have all kinds of chakras,

659
00:35:51,583 --> 00:35:54,000
you see, going into spasms.

660
00:35:55,542 --> 00:35:58,250
I am sometimes afraid of a puja in England.

661
00:36:01,999 --> 00:36:06,333
Gavin, I think you can just ...

662
00:36:14,333 --> 00:36:16,208
It's the mastery.

663
00:36:16,208 --> 00:36:17,875
You must have the mastery,

664
00:36:17,875 --> 00:36:19,417
upon yourself first of all.

665
00:36:19,417 --> 00:36:21,208
If you are not a master you cannot act

666
00:36:21,208 --> 00:36:24,083
- and upon your instrument, that's the point.

667
00:36:31,000 --> 00:36:33,917
And I would not like anybody to disrespect

668
00:36:33,917 --> 00:36:35,999
the leaders at all.

669
00:36:35,999 --> 00:36:39,208
You may be very intelligent, that's outside Sahaja Yoga.

670
00:36:39,542 --> 00:36:41,750
In Sahaja Yoga you have to listen to your leaders

671
00:36:41,750 --> 00:36:44,792
and respect, and nobody should try to find faults.

672
00:36:45,458 --> 00:36:47,999
I know his faults, what are his faults are,

673
00:36:47,999 --> 00:36:50,083
and I know how to deal with them.

674
00:36:50,333 --> 00:36:52,166
Everybody should try to strengthen.

675
00:36:52,166 --> 00:36:57,291
Now I would say in Australia, which is a modern thing,

676
00:36:57,542 --> 00:37:02,542
I should say that the whole thing works like one body.

677
00:37:03,750 --> 00:37:05,999
Nobody questions Warren.

678
00:37:06,667 --> 00:37:10,333
They telephone to him, they tell him, they collect money,

679
00:37:10,333 --> 00:37:13,875
they put the money - it's all working like one body.

680
00:37:13,875 --> 00:37:16,917
Here everybody is trying to cut the head

681
00:37:17,166 --> 00:37:18,250
- or attack the heart;

682
00:37:25,333 --> 00:37:27,667
that's your heart, that's your brain.

683
00:37:28,458 --> 00:37:33,000
So please remember all of you should offer services

684
00:37:33,667 --> 00:37:34,999
to Gavin,

685
00:37:35,208 --> 00:37:36,458
to Sahaja Yoga,

686
00:37:36,709 --> 00:37:38,750
before criticizing.

687
00:37:38,750 --> 00:37:40,500
Those who say the books are not arriving,

688
00:37:40,500 --> 00:37:43,125
let them take over the books.

689
00:37:44,792 --> 00:37:51,709
Even booking My seats and all that he has to run, I know;

690
00:37:51,959 --> 00:37:55,792
whatever you may say about ... he used to do all this.

691
00:37:57,583 --> 00:38:01,333
So you should offer your services also,

692
00:38:02,250 --> 00:38:03,709
to do these jobs.

693
00:38:03,709 --> 00:38:06,333
Otherwise Sahaja Yoga won't work out.

694
00:38:06,709 --> 00:38:08,917
We are not only here to take blessings

695
00:38:08,917 --> 00:38:11,375
but we have certain duties also,

696
00:38:11,375 --> 00:38:13,583
and that's what everybody should offer,

697
00:38:13,583 --> 00:38:17,667
their measure: what can I do, how can I help?

698
00:38:19,542 --> 00:38:22,125
What is the work? Let's see now.

699
00:38:24,458 --> 00:38:26,709
I hope in the next meeting you all should sit down

700
00:38:26,959 --> 00:38:28,917
and find out what you can do.

701
00:38:29,417 --> 00:38:32,792
A group can be formed: two, three persons can sit and do it

702
00:38:32,792 --> 00:38:35,333
with love, with attention,

703
00:38:35,917 --> 00:38:38,458
so that his burden will be reduced, and you will all feel

704
00:38:38,458 --> 00:38:40,709
the joy that you are doing something for Sahaja Yoga.

705
00:38:40,999 --> 00:38:42,417
Mother has done so much for you,

706
00:38:42,417 --> 00:38:44,542
what have you done for Sahaja Yoga?

707
00:38:46,542 --> 00:38:48,083
You want to have nice ashrams,

708
00:38:48,333 --> 00:38:49,709
nice place to live there,

709
00:38:49,999 --> 00:38:51,333
all right.

710
00:38:51,333 --> 00:38:53,792
You want to have comfortable places, cheaper places,

711
00:38:54,000 --> 00:38:55,083
all right.

712
00:38:55,417 --> 00:38:56,458
You want to have good health,

713
00:38:56,458 --> 00:38:57,417
all right.

714
00:38:57,417 --> 00:39:01,083
You want to have fine children, all right; enjoy your life.

715
00:39:02,458 --> 00:39:04,750
But what about giving,

716
00:39:06,542 --> 00:39:08,917
giving your heart,

717
00:39:09,667 --> 00:39:11,792
your respect?

718
00:39:14,000 --> 00:39:16,166
Next time when I come back,

719
00:39:16,458 --> 00:39:20,542
I want to see that you are all growing as one body.

720
00:39:20,792 --> 00:39:22,999
At least the Heart should be integrated,

721
00:39:23,208 --> 00:39:24,667
if nothing else.

722
00:39:24,917 --> 00:39:26,166
Imagine a heart

723
00:39:26,166 --> 00:39:28,999
which has the valves which pulsates at various times,

724
00:39:28,999 --> 00:39:34,333
all muscles going at different wavelengths.

725
00:39:35,083 --> 00:39:38,333
How can this universe survive with a heart like this?

726
00:39:40,542 --> 00:39:43,333
So I have to request all the,

727
00:39:43,583 --> 00:39:47,333
all the cells of the Heart to be alert,

728
00:39:47,333 --> 00:39:49,917
to be one in unison with God,

729
00:39:50,291 --> 00:39:52,875
and in loving care of the whole universe.

730
00:39:54,542 --> 00:39:56,458
May God bless you.

731
00:40:03,083 --> 00:40:05,542
So what is this puja supposed to be today?

732
00:40:07,417 --> 00:40:09,458
It's farewell puja

733
00:40:11,125 --> 00:40:13,250
today, so let's have it,

734
00:40:13,583 --> 00:40:15,709
just before the birth of Christ.

735
00:40:15,709 --> 00:40:18,333
Let Christ be born within us.

736
00:40:18,583 --> 00:40:20,999
Let's be, like Him,

737
00:40:20,999 --> 00:40:24,709
the one who always insisted,

738
00:40:25,458 --> 00:40:28,125
"Love your brothers. Love your sisters."

739
00:40:28,125 --> 00:40:30,000
Who are your brothers and sisters?

740
00:40:30,250 --> 00:40:31,667
He asked the question too,

741
00:40:31,917 --> 00:40:34,583
"Who are My brothers and sisters?"

742
00:40:35,125 --> 00:40:37,583
"Sahaja yogis are my brothers and sisters."

743
00:40:39,583 --> 00:40:41,291
Somebody offered at the altar.

744
00:40:41,291 --> 00:40:44,125
He said, "What are you to offer at the altar?

745
00:40:44,125 --> 00:40:46,625
Have you reconciled with your brother?"

746
00:40:46,917 --> 00:40:48,750
Have you reconciled?

747
00:40:49,166 --> 00:40:52,750
First reconcile, and then bring flowers to Mother.

748
00:40:55,625 --> 00:40:57,709
He said it already.

749
00:40:59,750 --> 00:41:02,917
Think of Him, how forgiving He was,

750
00:41:03,709 --> 00:41:06,834
how magnanimous, how great, and how

751
00:41:07,500 --> 00:41:09,750
He thought of His Father all the time,

752
00:41:09,750 --> 00:41:11,583
completely dedicated,

753
00:41:13,583 --> 00:41:15,291
doing His work.

754
00:41:18,166 --> 00:41:21,166
So with all praises to Christ

755
00:41:21,750 --> 00:41:23,917
and to His Mother who worked

756
00:41:24,166 --> 00:41:26,166
in a very potential manner,

757
00:41:27,625 --> 00:41:30,583
we have to today within ourselves

758
00:41:31,291 --> 00:41:34,166
awaken that great Spirit,

759
00:41:34,458 --> 00:41:37,583
which is actually the Aumkara.

760
00:41:41,959 --> 00:41:43,709
Even the memory,

761
00:41:43,709 --> 00:41:45,917
even the idea of that

762
00:41:46,709 --> 00:41:48,834
is so joy-giving.

763
00:41:50,291 --> 00:41:53,166
Let His life be reflected in your lives.

764
00:41:54,125 --> 00:41:57,917
You have to be true Christians.

765
00:42:05,834 --> 00:42:08,083
Let's have ... what is it? ....

766
00:42:11,208 --> 00:42:16,834
I think ... Now I would say, next time when you come to puja,

767
00:42:16,834 --> 00:42:18,542
all of you must have

768
00:42:18,792 --> 00:42:21,208
the hundred-and-eight names of the Goddess.

769
00:42:21,458 --> 00:42:23,583
You must have all the papers that are there.

770
00:42:23,834 --> 00:42:25,709
Like we have these books,

771
00:42:26,000 --> 00:42:28,583
all of us must have these papers,

772
00:42:28,834 --> 00:42:30,999
not only one person should have.

773
00:42:31,375 --> 00:42:34,125
We should try to remember certain things also:

774
00:42:34,375 --> 00:42:35,375
the names of the Goddess,

775
00:42:35,375 --> 00:42:37,208
the names that we recite.

776
00:42:37,208 --> 00:42:39,709
We should read them again and again and understand them,

777
00:42:39,709 --> 00:42:41,375
the Sanskrit meaning of it.

778
00:42:43,458 --> 00:42:45,250
And it should come to us very easily,

779
00:42:45,250 --> 00:42:48,583
because that is how we are going to work out our chakras.

780
00:42:50,083 --> 00:42:53,000
I don't think we have names of Christ,

781
00:42:53,000 --> 00:42:54,291
it's all right,

782
00:42:54,750 --> 00:42:57,417
and this time I hope we will try to

783
00:42:58,542 --> 00:43:00,542
read some names of Christ.

784
00:43:00,542 --> 00:43:03,999
But we have the names of Ganesha but not of Christ,

785
00:43:03,999 --> 00:43:07,917
so we'll say the hundred-and-eight names of Shri Ganesh,

786
00:43:08,208 --> 00:43:11,750
and somebody can wash My feet, all right ....

787
00:43:16,834 --> 00:43:17,875
Have you?

